Douglas Tait (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Douglas_Tait_(actor) 0 Douglas Tait (born December 17, 1978) is an American actor, stuntman, and independent filmmaker. Tait has played "monster" and creature characters in several films, including Star Trek, Zathura: A Space Adventure, Thor, Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull, and Land of the Lost.
